```typescript
const userId = 'current_user_id'; // Get from auth

const { data: userSimpleRecipes } = useQuery({
  queryKey: ['userSimpleRecipes', userId],
  queryFn: async () => {
    // Note: standalone_recipes needs user_id FK added in Phase 2 migration
    const { data, error } = await supabase
      .from('standalone_recipes')
      .select('*')
      .eq('source_type', 'user')
      .eq('user_id', userId) // Requires this column to exist
      .order('created_at', { ascending: false });
    if (error) throw error;
    return data || [];
  },
});
```

**If standalone_recipes doesn't have user_id yet:**
```sql
ALTER TABLE standalone_recipes
ADD COLUMN user_id UUID REFERENCES profiles(id) ON DELETE CASCADE;
```

